/ faqs
%section#faqs.section.p-t-0
  .container
    #accordion.panel-group
      .faqHeader General questions
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseOne"} Is account registration required?
        #collapseOne.panel-collapse.collapse.in
          .panel-body
            Account registration at
            %strong PrepBootstrap
            is only required if you will be selling or buying themes.
            This ensures a valid communication channel for all parties involved in any transactions.
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseTen"} Can I submit my own Bootstrap templates or themes?
        #collapseTen.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            A lot of the content of the site has been submitted by the community. Whether it is a commercial element/template/theme
            or a free one, you are encouraged to contribute. All credits are published along with the resources.
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseEleven"} What is the currency used for all transactions?
        #collapseEleven.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            All prices for themes, templates and other items, including each seller's or buyer's account balance are in
            %strong USD
      .faqHeader Sellers
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseTwo"} Who cen sell items?
        #collapseTwo.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            Any registed user, who presents a work, which is genuine and appealing, can post it on
            = succeed "." do
              %strong PrepBootstrap
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseThree"} I want to sell my items - what are the steps?
        #collapseThree.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            The steps involved in this process are really simple. All you need to do is:
            %ul
              %li Register an account
              %li Activate your account
              %li
                Go to the
                %strong Themes
                section and upload your theme
              %li The next step is the approval step, which usually takes about 72 hours.
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseFive"} How much do I get from each sale?
        #collapseFive.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            Here, at
            = succeed "," do
              %strong PrepBootstrap
            %br/
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseSix"} Why sell my items here?
        #collapseSix.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            There are a number of reasons why you should join us:
            %ul
              %li A great 70% flat rate for your items.
              %li Fast response/approval times. Many sites take weeks to process a theme or template. And if it gets rejected, there is another iteration. We have aliminated this, and made the process very fast. It only takes up to 72 hours for a template/theme to get reviewed.
              %li
                We are not an exclusive marketplace. This means that you can sell your items on
                = succeed "," do
                  %strong PrepBootstrap
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseEight"} What are the payment options?
        #collapseEight.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            The best way to transfer funds is via Paypal. This secure platform ensures timely payments and a secure environment.
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseNine"} When do I get paid?
        #collapseNine.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            Our standard payment plan provides for monthly payments. At the end of each month, all accumulated funds are transfered to your account.
            The minimum amount of your balance should be at least 70 USD.
      .faqHeader Buyers
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseFour"} I want to buy a theme - what are the steps?
        #collapseFour.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            Buying a theme on
            %strong PrepBootstrap
            is really simple. Each theme has a live preview.
            Once you have selected a theme or template, which is to your liking, you can quickly and securely pay via Paypal.
            %br/
            Once the transaction is complete, you gain full access to the purchased product.
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title
            %a.accordion-toggle.collapsed{"data-parent" => "#accordion", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :href => "#collapseSeven"} Is this the latest version of an item
        #collapseSeven.panel-collapse.collapse
          .panel-body
            Each item in
            %strong PrepBootstrap
            is maintained to its latest version. This ensures its smooth operation.
:css
  .faqHeader {
      font-size: 27px;
      margin: 20px;
  }

  .panel-heading [data-toggle="collapse"]:after {
      font-family: 'FontAwesome';
      content: "\f106"; /* "play" icon */
      float: right;
      color: #F58723;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 22px;
      /* rotate "play" icon from > (right arrow) to down arrow */
      -webkit-transform: rotate(180deg);
      -moz-transform: rotate(180deg);
      -ms-transform: rotate(180deg);
      -o-transform: rotate(180deg);
      transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .panel-heading [data-toggle="collapse"].collapsed:after {
      /* rotate "play" icon from > (right arrow) to ^ (up arrow) */
      -webkit-transform: rotate(90deg);
      -moz-transform: rotate(90deg);
      -ms-transform: rotate(90deg);
      -o-transform: rotate(90deg);
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      color: #454444;
  }
